<p>Hello! <%= @order.user.username %>, <br/>
Your order has been successfully placed. Total of the order is <%= @order.total %></p>
<h3>Order Summery</h3>
<h2><%= @order.order_number %></h2>
<p><%= @order.order_date %> INR<%= @order.total %></p>
